title: Dead Sea Scrolls - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 3/9/22

description:
George Noory and Dr. Ken Hanson discuss the discovery of new Dead Sea Scrolls, the most ancient version of the Hebrew Bible, and whether the new scrolls contain apocalyptic messages about the modern world.
